    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a peerless 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic, representing the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated S54 inline-six era. This specimen features six individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline, delivering linear power through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock. Comprehensive preventative maintenance has been executed, including a full VANOS overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity. The chassis remains taut with factory-spec geometry, refreshed bushings, and original dampers. With zero oxidation on the undercarriage and matching VIN tags on all panels, this is a concours-level example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection.",
